OOC: Alright, keep the insults to those that are absolutely necessary.  You 
disagree with someone, fine say you're wrong and this is why.  And no being a 
dumb idiot is not a valid reason.  I'm going to be honest and say that I 
dislike wrestling in general and am wary of it being brought into the game in 
any manner.  That said, I also think that the faction has potential and I'm 
going to keep my personal feelings out of it for the moment.  We shall see 
how this turns out.

--part1_189.c972317.2a8fc694_boundary
